### Multi-Tenant SaaS API - Tenants
### VS Code REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client compatible

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get tokens first by running auth.http login
@accessToken = {{$dotenv %ACCESS_TOKEN}}
@tenantId = {{$dotenv %TENANT_ID}}

### Create a new tenant
# @name createTenant
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "New Organization"
}

### Get current tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/current
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Update current tenant
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/current
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Updated Organization Name"
}

### Get tenant members
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/current/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}

### Get tenant by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get tenant by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/slug/my-organization
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
